headline: Northrop Grumman (NOC) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Northrop Grumman (NOC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +3.27% and +0.83%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: 1 Volatile Stock on Our Buy List and 2 We Find Risky
summary: Market swings can be tough to stomach, and volatile stocks often experience exaggerated moves in both directions. While many thrive during risk-on environments, many also struggle to maintain investor confidence when the ride gets bumpy.
